{"tid":1987308,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[郭偉健]官指不會考慮旺角騷亂背景10被告暴動罪成　最重囚4年3月","createTime":"2020-04-24T11:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T17:59:03.000Z","uid":59518,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2b1ed93e6ee5dd21eab6262662de747048b907b2","tid":1987308,"uid":59518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:28:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180601/20407791\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180601%2F20407791&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabknw%2BoCD4UrwaevtQIqI6x5z0%3D&h=09afa8e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180601%2F20407791&h=9d96b921\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180601/20407791</a><br />\n<br />\n辯方早前求情指應考慮當時社會及暴亂發生的背景，包括市民支持無牌小販、中港矛盾、雨傘運動期間警方濫權、貧富懸殊及高樓價，事件是對政府施政失效的抗議，郭官質疑此說有如「走後門」，若有兩人分別因政治因素及貪玩而干犯相同暴力行為，但因前者稱參與政治遊行獲輕判，實屬完全不合邏輯，等同叫法庭對政治議題作出評論及判斷。法庭絕不會加入這種政治辯論，更不會評定政治的對錯。"},{"pid":"9c913495ddfe9180830dccb9d8b1f688db935a35","tid":1987308,"uid":240362,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:29:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">法庭絕不會加入這種政治辯論，更不會評定政治的對錯。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"a900bba5f15b8e484273b05cd834f736004cb132","tid":1987308,"uid":240362,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"9c913495ddfe9180830dccb9d8b1f688db935a35","tid":1987308,"uid":240362,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:29:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">法庭絕不會加入這種政治辯論，更不會評定政治的對錯。</span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:29:48.000Z","msg":"今日又咁長篇大論"},{"pid":"bf12b8f338b3e2daeb8b1b3d72e596de6cb30ae8","tid":1987308,"uid":127929,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:30:55.000Z","msg":"紅官潛台詞：只要你係支持中國, 你就可以斬人冇後果"},{"pid":"14afb56c8551c6f6d339ba9a2b6372